sequenceDiagram
  actor U as user
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant SB as Supabase Auth
  participant M as Resend (E-Mail)
  participant BE as Backend
  U->>FE: E-Mail eingeben
  FE->>SB: signInWithOtp(email)
  SB->>M: 6-stelligen Code senden
  M-->>U: E-Mail mit Code
  U->>FE: Code eingeben
  FE->>SB: verifyOtp(code)
  SB-->>FE: Access- + Refresh-Token (JWT, RS256)
  FE->>FE: speichert im localStorage
  FE->>BE: GET /api/decks  +  Bearer JWT
  BE->>SB: JWKS holen
  BE->>BE: JWT prüfen
  BE-->>FE: 200 OK + Daten
